[slide]
# HTML
## What is HTML?

0. `HTML` stands for _HyperText Markup Language_
0. `HTML` is used for creating web pages
0. `HTML` uses *tags* to create a document structure _(similar to XML)_
0. Web browsers use markup to determine how to display a page



[slide]
# HTML
## Browsers

There are hundreds of web browsers, but only a handful of popular ones.

0. Chrome
0. Firefox
0. Internet Explorer
0. Safari
0. Opera



