[slide]
# HTML
## Text

Most text will appear as normal when entered into HTML

<pre class="code html" >
Hello, World!
</pre>

<div class="output" >
Hello, World!
</div>


[slide]
# HTML
## Newlines

Newlines will not cause line breaks.

<pre class="code html" >
Hello,


World!
</pre>

<div class="output" >
Hello,


World!
</div>



[slide]
# HTML
## Spaces

Multiple spaces in a row are ignored.

<pre class="code html" >
Hello,           World!
</pre>

<div class="output" >
Hello,           World!
</div>

